ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:28:18.000Z","msg":"香港人 團結"},{"pid":"b452d2c99494f50bb6e39a00d4aa6a419dc02feb","tid":1747411,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"39e64ed2ed213f44b364f9c41989eb68006ad9a6","tid":1747411,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［請廣傳］<br />\n和理非目前可以做到嘅事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最迫切：區選投票！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一.）強烈建議香港人<span style=\"color: red;\">即時停止再月捐所有喺今次革命奶共/ 無幫過香港人嘅NGO組織</span>，將啲錢用喺更加有用嘅地方上面，例如揸車接放學嘅油費、飯券、法庭訟費、醫療開支、FA嘅物資費用等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奶共/ 無幫過香港人嘅NGO組織例子：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: gold;\">宣明會</span><br />\n（2018善款超過9.1億）：有巴絲post CUT捐回覆，「oh好遺憾」<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\">無國界醫生</span><br />\n（2017總收入超5億）：有巴絲post非新聞稿答覆，達哥式回應（一直有mon住關注情況，屌你你mon到香港淪陷埋先出手不如）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（無恥界醫生條熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut）</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: gold;\">樂施會</span><br />\n（2017總收入超2.5億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: gold;\">奧比斯香港</span><br />\n（2018年總收入超2.1億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: gold;\">UNICEF HK</span><br />\n（2017年總收入超1.7億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: gold;\">Save the Children</span><br />\n （2017年總收入超1.6億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n7. <span style=\"color: gold;\">香港紅十字會</span><br />\n（2017/18年總收入超1.4億）：18/8出咗份聲明，借世界人道主義日輕輕帶過呼籲各方克制，過去兩個多月動員逾800人次做電話熱線加現場支援<a href=\"https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/press_room/press_release_2019/201908182.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redcross.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fpress_room%2Fpress_release_2019%2F201908182.html&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=d6e239a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/press_room/press_release_2019/201908182.html</a><br />\n8. <span style=\"color: gold;\">國際培幼會</span><br />\n（2017年總收入近8000萬）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二.）本地文宣上，各區連儂牆近日被大肆清拆，各位香港人可以喺朝早人多時份重建連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三.）持續喺國際文宣上着力（Twitter, FB, IG），呼籲國際社會支持香港示威者五大訴求，順便將黑警惡行/ 中共建政70年嚟種種歷史惡行公諸於世"},{"pid":"78efd5f52d0294090f598a5d5574b9d2e675d058","tid":1747411,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:57:14.000Z","msg":"香港人團結"},{"pid":"890833c1c95ea8ea82eceae0659c852b103fd810","tid":1747411,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"香城online玩家大型活動 投票Challenge<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"feec70bd2fdbd75837fb875eeb52420db3df09b7","tid":1747411,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"香港人 團結"},{"pid":"5df7887b5832aa3fb5dcccef0c5790ae901b3d75","tid":1747411,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"香港人 團結"},{"pid":"07d15844414c02692f52e563bbc3a2dd4d69a011","tid":1747411,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:59:25.000Z","msg":"香港人 團結"},{"pid":"9de707dcc56cb490fa538541b30c357387bb1e44","tid":1747411,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:37:53.000Z","msg":"香港人 團結"}]}